THIS FRIDAY - 24 Sept: Join us in our #DMRCFridays. In this online seminar, @andairamf,@rosalie_gillett
, &amp; @ZahraStardust discuss online harm and the discrepancies between how users and platforms conceptualise the problem. More info: https://t.co/hHGy1M989T 
@QUT @AdmsCentre

Congratulations to DMRC’s @timothyjgraham 
who has been awarded an @arc_gov_au DECRA 2022 for his project "Combatting Coordinated Inauthentic Behaviour on Social Media." Read more about this project here: https://t.co/SDD4HN15z0
@QUT #qutcreativeindustries https://t.co/3MG88gKjMX

Our next #DataScience 'Under the Hood' webinar is on Fri 29 May. Dr Timothy Graham will be sharing fundamental &amp; cutting-edge data science methods on 'Detecting and analysing coordinated inauthentic behaviour on #socialmedia '
https://t.co/DWhXSX48l1
@Timothyjgraham @qutdmrc https://t.co/UuEVckzpCl

